{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775870973801,"sessionID":"ses_285d8262dffe6kzNvkjnUFKpyR","part":{"id":"prt_d7a289767001TLQoONF8Luvalq","messageID":"msg_d7a287c83001mQ33mTonvmtje6","sessionID":"ses_285d8262dffe6kzNvkjnUFKpyR","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775871087594,"sessionID":"ses_285d8262dffe6kzNvkjnUFKpyR","part":{"id":"prt_d7a2a53570017M9yFe7Y00u4p3","messageID":"msg_d7a287c83001mQ33mTonvmtje6","sessionID":"ses_285d8262dffe6kzNvkjnUFKpyR","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-7f0c043f78724aaab17c5fba9fca9a0b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-024 — DockerService 封装 (DockerService Encapsulation)\n\n## 模块信息\n\n- **模块**: `cmd/cli`\n- **语言**: Python\n- **规模**: M\n- **关联需求**: AR-024\n\n## 架构概述\n\n### 设计目标\n\nDockerService 是一个封装了 Docker SDK 操作的服务类，为 AgentCube CLI 的构建和发布工作流提供统一的 Docker 接口。该服务封装了 Docker SDK 的复杂性，提供了简洁的高级 API 用于镜像构建、推送、标记和管理等操作，同时提供完善的错误处理、日志记录和输入验证机制。\n\n### 核心组件\n\n```\nagentcube/services/\n├── docker_service.py         # DockerService 主要实现\n├── __init__.py               # 服务包导出\n└── [exceptions.py]           # 自定义异常类（可选）\n```\n\n### 架构原则\n\n1. **封装复杂性**: 将 Docker SDK 的复杂性封装在服务层，提供简洁的高级 API\n2. **延迟初始化**: Docker 客户端采用延迟初始化（Lazy Initialization）模式\n3. **错误隔离**: 将 Docker SDK 异常包装为服务特定异常，避免直接暴露底层实现\n4. **安全第一**: 妥善处理敏感信息（如密码），不记录到日志中\n5. **可观测性**: 提供可选的详细日志模式，支持调试和故障排查\n6. **幂等性**: 所有操作设计为幂等的，可以安全地重复执行\n\n## 组件设计\n\n### DockerService 类\n\n#### 数据结构\n\n```python\nimport logging\nimport time\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any, Dict, Optional\n\nimport docker\nfrom docker.errors import DockerException\n\n\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\n\nclass DockerService:\n    \"\"\"Service for Docker operations.\"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None:\n        \"\"\"Initialize the Docker service.\n\n        Args:\n            verbose: Enable verbose logging for debugging.\n\n        Raises:\n            RuntimeError: If Docker client initialization fails.\n        \"\"\"\n        self.verbose = verbose\n        if verbose:\n            logging.basicConfig(level=logging.DEBUG)\n        self._client: Optional[docker.DockerClient] = None\n\n    @property\n    def client(self) -> docker.DockerClient:\n        \"\"\"Get or create Docker client using lazy initialization.\n\n        Returns:\n            The Docker client instance.\n\n        Raises:\n            DockerException: If Docker daemon is not available.\n        \"\"\"\n        if self._client is None:\n            self._client = docker.from_env()\n        return self._client\n```\n\n#### 公共 API 方法\n\n##### 1. Docker 可用性检查\n\n```python\ndef check_docker_available(self) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"Check if Docker daemon is available and running.\n\n    Returns:\n        True if Docker is available, False otherwise.\n\n    Note:\n        This method does not raise exceptions on failure, making it\n        suitable for availability checks before operations.\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        self.client.ping()\n        return True\n    except DockerException as e:\n        logger.warning(f\"Docker not available: {e}\")\n        return False\n```\n\n##### 2. 镜像构建\n\n```python\ndef build_image(\n    self,\n    dockerfile_path: Path,\n    context_path: Path,\n    image_name: str,\n    tag: str = \"latest\",\n    build_args: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"Build a Docker image from a Dockerfile.\n\n    Args:\n        dockerfile_path: Path to the Dockerfile.\n        context_path: Path to the build context directory.\n        image_name: Name for the resulting image.\n        tag: Tag for the image (default: \"latest\").\n        build_args: Optional build arguments for proxy configuration.\n\n    Returns:\n        Dict containing:\n            - image_name: Full image name with tag.\n            - image_id: SHA256 hash of the image.\n            - image_size: Human-readable size string.\n            - size_bytes: Size in bytes.\n            - build_time: Timestamp of the build.\n\n    Raises:\n        FileNotFoundError: If dockerfile_path or context_path does not exist.\n        ValueError: If image_name or dockerfile_path is invalid.\n        RuntimeError: If Docker is not available or build fails.\n    \"\"\"\n    if not self.check_docker_available():\n        raise RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")\n\n    logger.info(f\"Building image {image_name}:{tag} from {dockerfile_path}\")\n    full_image_name = f\"{image_name}:{tag}\"\n\n    try:\n        image, build_logs = self.client.images.build(\n            path=str(context_path),\n            dockerfile=str(dockerfile_path),\n            tag=full_image_name,\n            buildargs=build_args,\n            rm=True,\n            forcerm=True,\n        )\n\n        image_info = self.get_image_info(full_image_name)\n        image_info[\"build_time\"] = time.time()\n\n        return image_info\n\n    except DockerException as e:\n        raise RuntimeError(f\"Failed to build Docker image: {e}\") from e\n```\n\n##### 3. 镜像信息查询\n\n```python\ndef get_image_info(self, image_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"Get detailed information about a Docker image.\n\n    Args:\n        image_name: Name of the image (with or without tag).\n\n    Returns:\n        Dict containing:\n            - image_name: The image name.\n            - image_id: SHA256 hash (first 12 characters).\n            - image_size: Human-readable size string.\n            - size_bytes: Size in bytes.\n\n    Note:\n        Returns empty dict if image is not found.\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        image = self.client.images.get(image_name)\n        attrs = image.attrs\n\n        image_id = attrs[\"Id\"].split(\":\")[-1][:12]\n        size_bytes = attrs.get(\"Size\", 0)\n\n        return {\n            \"image_name\": image_name,\n            \"image_id\": image_id,\n            \"image_size\": self._format_size(size_bytes),\n            \"size_bytes\": size_bytes,\n        }\n\n    except DockerException as e:\n        logger.warning(f\"Failed to get image info for {image_name}: {e}\")\n        return {}\n```\n\n##### 4. 镜像推送\n\n```python\ndef push_image(\n    self,\n    image_name: str,\n    registry_url: Optional[str] = None,\n    username: Optional[str] = None,\n    password: Optional[str] = None,\n) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"Push a Docker image to a container registry.\n\n    Args:\n        image_name: Local image name to push.\n        registry_url: Optional registry URL (e.g., \"registry.example.com/username\").\n        username: Optional username for private registry authentication.\n        password: Optional password for private registry authentication.\n\n    Returns:\n        Dict containing:\n            - pushed_image: Full name of the pushed image.\n            - push_time: Timestamp of the push operation.\n\n    Raises:\n        RuntimeError: If Docker is not available, authentication fails,\n                     or push operation fails.\n        ValueError: If image does not exist locally.\n\n    Security Note:\n        Passwords are never logged or stored in instance variables.\n    \"\"\"\n    if not self.check_docker_available():\n        raise RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")\n\n    target_image = image_name\n    if registry_url:\n        target_image = f\"{registry_url}/{image_name}\"\n        self._tag_image_sdk(image_name, target_image)\n\n    if username and password:\n        self._docker_login_sdk(registry_url, username, password)\n\n    logger.info(f\"Pushing image {target_image}\")\n\n    try:\n        push_logs = self.client.images.push(target_image, stream=True, decode=True)\n\n        for line in push_logs:\n            if \"error\" in line:\n                raise RuntimeError(f\"Failed to push image: {line['error']}\")\n            if self.verbose:\n                logger.debug(f\"Push log: {line}\")\n\n        return {\n            \"pushed_image\": target_image,\n            \"push_time\": str(time.time()),\n        }\n\n    except DockerException as e:\n        raise RuntimeError(f\"Failed to push Docker image: {e}\") from e\n```\n\n##### 5. 镜像删除\n\n```python\ndef remove_image(self, image_name: str, force: bool = True) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"Remove a Docker image from the local daemon.\n\n    Args:\n        image_name: Name of the image to remove.\n        force: Force removal even if image is in use (default: True).\n\n    Returns:\n        True if removal succeeded, False otherwise.\n\n    Note:\n        This method does not raise exceptions for non-existent images,\n        making it safe for cleanup operations.\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        self.client.images.remove(image_name, force=force)\n        logger.info(f\"Removed image {image_name}\")\n        return True\n    except DockerException as e:\n        logger.warning(f\"Failed to remove image {image_name}: {e}\")\n        return False\n```\n\n#### 私有辅助方法\n\n##### 1. Docker registry 登录\n\n```python\ndef _docker_login_sdk(self, registry: Optional[str], username: str, password: str) -> None:\n    \"\"\"Log in to a Docker registry.\n\n    Args:\n        registry: Registry URL or None for Docker Hub.\n        username: Username for authentication.\n        password: Password for authentication.\n\n    Raises:\n        RuntimeError: If authentication fails.\n\n    Security Note:\n        Password is never logged. Authentication is handled\n        securely through Docker SDK.\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        self.client.login(username=username, password=password, registry=registry)\n        logger.info(f\"Successfully logged in to registry: {registry or 'default'}\")\n    except DockerException as e:\n        raise RuntimeError(f\"Failed to log in to Docker registry: {e}\") from e\n```\n\n##### 2. 镜像标记\n\n```python\ndef _tag_image_sdk(self, source_image: str, target_image: str) -> None:\n    \"\"\"Tag a Docker image with a new name.\n\n    Args:\n        source_image: Existing image name.\n        target_image: New image name/tag.\n\n    Raises:\n        RuntimeError: If tagging fails.\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        image = self.client.images.get(source_image)\n        image.tag(target_image, force=True)\n        logger.info(f\"Tagged {source_image} as {target_image}\")\n    except DockerException as e:\n        raise RuntimeError(f\"Failed to tag Docker image: {e}\") from e\n```\n\n##### 3. 大小格式化\n\n```python\ndef _format_size(self, size_bytes: int) -> str:\n    \"\"\"Format byte size into human-readable format.\n\n    Args:\n        size_bytes: Size in bytes.\n\n    Returns:\n        Human-readable size string (e.g., \"2.00 GB\").\n\n    Example:\n        >>> self._format_size(2147483648)\n        \"2.00 GB\"\n    \"\"\"\n    size = float(size_bytes)\n    for unit in [\"B\", \"KB\", \"MB\", \"GB\"]:\n        if size < 1024:\n            return f\"{size:.2f} {unit}\"\n        size /= 1024\n    return f\"{size:.2f} TB\"\n```\n\n## 数据流\n\n### 镜像构建流程\n\n```\n┌─────────────────┐\n│ BuildRuntime    │\n│ (调用方)        │\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n         ▼\n┌─────────────────┐\n│ build_image()   │\n│ DockerService   │\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n         ├─────────────────────────────────┐\n         │                                 │\n         ▼                                 ▼\n┌─────────────────┐              ┌─────────────────┐\n│ check_docker_   │              │ validate_paths()│\n│ available()     │              │                 │\n└────────┬────────┘              └────────┬────────┘\n         │                                 │\n         ▼                                 ▼\n     ┌────┴────┐                    ┌──────┴──────┐\n     │         │                    │             │\n     ▼         ▼                    ▼             ▼\n ┌──────┐  ┌──────┐           ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐\n │可用? │  │不可用?│          │路径有效? │  │路径无效? │\n └───┬──┘  └───┬──┘           └────┬─────┘  └────┬─────┘\n     │          │                    │             │\n     ▼          ▼                    ▼             ▼\n ┌──────┐  ┌──────┐            ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐\n │继续  │  │抛出   │            │调用      │  │抛出      │\n │构建  │  │Runtime│            │Docker    │  │FileNotFound│\n └───┬──┘  └──────┘            │SDK.build │  └──────────┘\n     │                       └────┬─────┘\n     │                            │\n     ▼                            ▼\n┌─────────────────┐      ┌─────────────────┐\n│ get_image_info()│      │ 流式输出日志    │\n│                 │      │ (verbose模式)   │\n└────────┬────────┘      └─────────────────┘\n         │\n         ▼\n┌─────────────────┐\n│ 返回结果dict    │\n│ (image_id,      │\n│  size, time)    │\n└─────────────────┘\n```\n\n### 镜像推送流程\n\n```\n┌─────────────────┐\n│ PublishRuntime  │\n│ (调用方)        │\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n         ▼\n┌─────────────────┐\n│ push_image()    │\n│ DockerService   │\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n         ├─────────────────────────────────┐\n         │                                 │\n         ▼                                 ▼\n┌─────────────────┐              ┌─────────────────┐\n│ check_docker_   │              │ validate_image()│\n│ available()     │              │                 │\n└────────┬────────┘              └────────┬────────┘\n         │                                 │\n         ▼                                 ▼\n     ┌────┴────┐                    ┌──────┴──────┐\n     │         │                    │             │\n     ▼         ▼                    ▼             ▼\n ┌──────┐  ┌──────┐           ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐\n │可用? │  │不可用?│          │镜像存在? │  │镜像不存在?│\n └───┬──┘  └───┬──┘           └────┬─────┘  └────┬─────┘\n     │          │                    │             │\n     ▼          ▼                    ▼             ▼\n ┌──────┐  ┌──────┐            ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐\n │检查  │  │抛出   │            │检查      │  │抛出      │\n │registry│ │Runtime│            │是否需要  │  │ValueError│\n │URL?   │  │Error  │            │重新标记  │  │          │\n └───┬──┘  └──────┘            └────┬─────┘  └──────────┘\n     │                            │\n     ▼                            ▼\n┌──────────┐              ┌───────────────┐\n│需要登录? │              │ _tag_image_sdk│\n└────┬─────┘              └───────┬───────┘\n     │                            │\n  ┌──┴──┐                         ▼\n  │     │                    ┌──────────────┐\n  ▼     ▼                    │需要认证?     │\n┌────┐ ┌────┐                └────┬─────────┘\n│是  │ │否  │                     │\n└┬───┘ └┬──┘                  ┌────┴────┐\n │     │                      │         │\n ▼     ▼                      ▼         ▼\n┌─────────┐              ┌─────────┐ ┌─────────┐\n│_docker_ │              │是       │ │否       │\n│login_sdk│              └────┬────┘ └────┬────┘\n└────┬────┘                   │           │\n     │                       ▼           ▼\n     ▼                  ┌─────────┐  ┌─────────┐\n┌─────────┐             │_docker_ │  │调用     │\n│调用     │             │login_sdk│  │Docker   │\n│Docker   │             └────┬────┘  │SDK.push │\n│SDK.push │                  │       └────┬────┘\n└────┬────┘                  ▼            │\n     │                 ┌─────────┐        │\n     ▼                 │调用     │        │\n┌─────────┐            │Docker   │        ▼\n│流式输出 │            │SDK.push │  ┌─────────────┐\n│日志     │            └────┬────┘  │验证推送结果 │\n│(verbose)│                 │       └──────┬──────┘\n└─────────┘                 ▼              │\n                   ┌─────────────┐          │\n                   │流式输出日志  │          │\n                   │(verbose)     │          ▼\n                   └─────────────┘  ┌─────────────┐\n                                    │返回结果dict │\n                                    └─────────────┘\n```\n\n## 序列图\n\n### 成功构建镜像\n\n```\nBuildRuntime    DockerService    Docker Client    Docker Daemon\n     │                 │                 │                  │\n     │ build_image()   │                 │                  │\n     │────────────────►│                 │                  │\n     │                 │ check_docker_   │                  │\n     │                 │ available()     │                  │\n     │                 │────────────────►│                  │\n     │                 │                 │ ping()           │\n     │                 │                 │─────────────────►│\n     │                 │                 │◄─────────────────│\n     │                 │◄────────────────│                  │\n     │                 │ images.build()  │                  │\n     │                 │────────────────►│                  │\n     │                 │                 │ build context    │\n     │                 │                 │─────────────────►│\n     │                 │                 │◄─────────────────│\n     │                 │                 │ (stream logs)    │\n     │                 │◄────────────────│                  │\n     │                 │ get_image_info()│                  │\n     │                 │────────────────►│                  │\n     │                 │                 │ images.get()     │\n     │                 │                 │─────────────────►│\n     │                 │                 │◄─────────────────│\n     │                 │◄────────────────│                  │\n     │◄────────────────│                 │                  │\n     │  result dict    │                 │                  │\n```\n\n### 推送镜像到私有仓库\n\n```\nPublishRuntime  DockerService    Docker Client    Docker Daemon   Registry\n      │                │                 │                  │           │\n      │ push_image()   │                 │                  │           │\n      │───────────────►│                 │                  │           │\n      │                │ check_docker_   │                  │           │\n      │                │ available()     │                  │           │\n      │                │────────────────►│                  │           │\n      │                │                 │ ping()           │           │\n      │                │                 │─────────────────►│           │\n      │                │                 │◄─────────────────│           │\n      │                │◄────────────────│                  │           │\n      │                │ _tag_image_sdk()│                  │           │\n      │                │────────────────►│                  │           │\n      │                │                 │ image.tag()      │           │\n      │                │                 │─────────────────►│           │\n      │                │                 │◄─────────────────│           │\n      │                │◄────────────────│                  │           │\n      │                │ _docker_login_  │                  │           │\n      │                │ sdk()           │                  │           │\n      │                │────────────────►│                  │           │\n      │                │                 │ login()          │           │\n      │                │                 │─────────────────────────────►│\n      │                │                 │◄─────────────────────────────│\n      │                │◄────────────────│                  │           │\n      │                │ images.push()   │                  │           │\n      │                │────────────────►│                  │           │\n      │                │                 │ push layers      │           │\n      │                │                 │─────────────────────────────►│\n      │                │                 │◄─────────────────────────────│\n      │                │                 │ (stream logs)    │           │\n      │                │◄────────────────│                  │           │\n      │◄───────────────│                 │                  │           │\n      │  result dict   │                 │                  │           │\n```\n\n## 错误处理\n\n### 错误分类\n\n| 错误类型 | 异常类 | 触发场景 | 处理策略 |\n|---------|--------|---------|---------|\n| Docker 不可用 | `RuntimeError` | `check_docker_available()` 返回 `False` | 操作前检查，提供清晰错误信息 |\n| 文件不存在 | `FileNotFoundError` | dockerfile_path 或 context_path 不存在 | 验证输入路径，提供路径信息 |\n| 镜像不存在 | `ValueError` | 尝试操作不存在的镜像 | 验证镜像存在性 |\n| 构建失败 | `RuntimeError` | Docker 构建过程失败 | 包装 Docker SDK 异常 |\n| 认证失败 | `RuntimeError` | Registry 认证失败 | 不记录密码，提供通用错误信息 |\n| 网络错误 | `RuntimeError` | Registry 不可达 | 提供网络相关信息 |\n| 标记失败 | `RuntimeError` | 镜像标记失败 | 提供源/目标镜像名称 |\n\n### 异常处理策略\n\n```python\ndef _handle_docker_exception(self, operation: str, exception: DockerException) -> None:\n    \"\"\"Handle Docker SDK exceptions with context.\n\n    Args:\n        operation: Name of the operation being performed.\n        exception: The Docker SDK exception.\n\n    Raises:\n        RuntimeError: Wrapped exception with additional context.\n    \"\"\"\n    error_msg = f\"Docker {operation} failed: {str(exception)}\"\n    logger.error(error_msg)\n    raise RuntimeError(error_msg) from exception\n```\n\n### 错误恢复机制\n\n1. **客户端重连**: 如果 Docker 守护进程重启，客户端属性会重新初始化\n2. **幂等操作**: 所有操作设计为可安全重试\n3. **非关键失败**: `remove_image()` 等操作失败不抛出异常，仅返回 `False`\n\n## 安全考虑\n\n### 凭证处理\n\n```python\ndef _docker_login_sdk(self, registry: Optional[str], username: str, password: str) -> None:\n    \"\"\"Secure login to Docker registry.\n\n    Security Measures:\n        1. Password is never logged or stored in instance variables.\n        2. Uses Docker SDK's secure authentication mechanism.\n        3. Password is only held in memory during the login call.\n        4. Log messages use placeholders for sensitive data.\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        # Password is only passed to Docker SDK, never logged\n        self.client.login(username=username, password=password, registry=registry)\n\n        # Log success without revealing credentials\n        registry_name = registry or \"Docker Hub\"\n        logger.info(f\"Successfully logged in to registry: {registry_name}\")\n    except DockerException as e:\n        # Error message does not include password\n        raise RuntimeError(\n            f\"Failed to log in to Docker registry '{registry or 'Docker Hub'}': {e}\"\n        ) from e\n```\n\n### 路径验证\n\n```python\ndef _validate_build_paths(self, dockerfile_path: Path, context_path: Path) -> None:\n    \"\"\"Validate file paths before Docker operations.\n\n    Security Measures:\n        1. Resolves absolute paths to prevent directory traversal.\n        2. Validates paths exist before operations.\n        3. Validates context_path is a directory.\n        4. Validates dockerfile_path is a file.\n\n    Raises:\n        FileNotFoundError: If paths do not exist.\n        ValueError: If paths have invalid types.\n    \"\"\"\n    dockerfile_path = dockerfile_path.resolve()\n    context_path = context_path.resolve()\n\n    if not dockerfile_path.exists():\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"Dockerfile not found: {dockerfile_path}\")\n    if not dockerfile_path.is_file():\n        raise ValueError(f\"Dockerfile path is not a file: {dockerfile_path}\")\n\n    if not context_path.exists():\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"Build context not found: {context_path}\")\n    if not context_path.is_dir():\n        raise ValueError(f\"Build context path is not a directory: {context_path}\")\n```\n\n### 日志安全\n\n```python\n# Good: No sensitive information\nlogger.info(f\"Pushing image {target_image}\")\nlogger.info(f\"Successfully logged in to registry: {registry_name}\")\n\n# Bad: Never log passwords\n# logger.info(f\"Logging in with password: {password}\")  # DON'T DO THIS\n```\n\n## API 契约\n\n### 公共 API 摘要\n\n| 方法 | 输入参数 | 返回值 | 可能抛出 |\n|------|---------|--------|---------|\n| `__init__` | `verbose: bool = False` | `DockerService` 实例 | `RuntimeError` |\n| `check_docker_available` | - | `bool` | - |\n| `build_image` | `dockerfile_path`, `context_path`, `image_name`, `tag`, `build_args` | `Dict[str, Any]` | `RuntimeError`, `FileNotFoundError`, `ValueError` |\n| `get_image_info` | `image_name` | `Dict[str, Any]` | - |\n| `push_image` | `image_name`, `registry_url`, `username`, `password` | `Dict[str, Any]` | `RuntimeError`, `ValueError` |\n| `remove_image` | `image_name`, `force` | `bool` | - |\n\n### 返回值结构\n\n#### build_image() 返回值\n\n```python\n{\n    \"image_name\": \"myagent:latest\",\n    \"image_id\": \"abc123def456\",\n    \"image_size\": \"2.00 GB\",\n    \"size_bytes\": 2147483648,\n    \"build_time\": 1712851200.123456\n}\n```\n\n#### push_image() 返回值\n\n```python\n{\n    \"pushed_image\": \"registry.example.com/username/myagent:latest\",\n    \"push_time\": \"1712851200.123456\"\n}\n```\n\n#### get_image_info() 返回值\n\n```python\n{\n    \"image_name\": \"myagent:latest\",\n    \"image_id\": \"abc123def456\",\n    \"image_size\": \"2.00 GB\",\n    \"size_bytes\": 2147483648\n}\n```\n\n## 依赖项\n\n| 依赖 | 版本 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `docker` | `>=6.0.0` | Docker SDK for Python |\n| `pathlib` | - | 文件路径处理（标准库） |\n| `logging` | - | 日志记录（标准库） |\n| `typing` | - | 类型注解（标准库） |\n| `time` | - | 时间戳（标准库） |\n\n### Docker SDK 依赖\n\nDockerService 依赖 `docker.from_env()` 初始化客户端，该函数会自动：\n\n1. 从环境变量 `DOCKER_HOST` 读取 Docker daemon 地址\n2. 使用默认的 Unix socket 或 Windows named pipe\n3. 支持环境变量配置：\n   - `DOCKER_HOST`: Docker daemon 地址\n   - `DOCKER_TLS_VERIFY`: TLS 验证\n   - `DOCKER_CERT_PATH`: 证书路径\n\n## 测试策略\n\n### 单元测试\n\n#### 测试覆盖率目标\n\n- **行覆盖率**: ≥ 90%\n- **分支覆盖率**: ≥ 85%\n\n#### 测试用例分类\n\n**1. 初始化测试**\n\n```python\ndef test_docker_service_init_verbose():\n    \"\"\"Test DockerService initialization with verbose=True.\"\"\"\n    service = DockerService(verbose=True)\n    assert service.verbose is True\n    assert service._client is None  # Lazy initialization\n\ndef test_docker_service_init_non_verbose():\n    \"\"\"Test DockerService initialization with verbose=False.\"\"\"\n    service = DockerService(verbose=False)\n    assert service.verbose is False\n```\n\n**2. 可用性检查测试**\n\n```python\ndef test_check_docker_available_success():\n    \"\"\"Test successful Docker availability check.\"\"\"\n    with mock.patch('docker.from_env') as mock_docker:\n        mock_client = mock.Mock()\n        mock_docker.return_value = mock_client\n        mock_client.ping.return_value = True\n\n        service = DockerService()\n        assert service.check_docker_available() is True\n\ndef test_check_docker_available_failure():\n    \"\"\"Test failed Docker availability check.\"\"\"\n    with mock.patch('docker.from_env') as mock_docker:\n        mock_client = mock.Mock()\n        mock_docker.return_value = mock_client\n        mock_client.ping.side_effect = DockerException(\"Connection failed\")\n\n        service = DockerService()\n        assert service.check_docker_available() is False\n```\n\n**3. 镜像构建测试**\n\n```python\ndef test_build_image_success():\n    \"\"\"Test successful image build.\"\"\"\n    with mock.patch('docker.from_env') as mock_docker:\n        mock_client = mock.Mock()\n        mock_docker.return_value = mock_client\n\n        mock_image = mock.Mock()\n        mock_image.attrs = {\n            'Id': 'sha256:abcdef123456',\n            'Size': 1024 * 1024  # 1 MB\n        }\n        mock_client.images.build.return_value = (mock_image, [])\n\n        service = DockerService()\n        result = service.build_image(\n            dockerfile_path=Path(\"Dockerfile\"),\n            context_path=Path(\".\"),\n            image_name=\"test-image\"\n        )\n\n        assert result['image_name'] == \"test-image:latest\"\n        assert result['image_id'] == \"abcdef123456\"\n        assert \"build_time\" in result\n\ndef test_build_image_docker_unavailable():\n    \"\"\"Test build failure when Docker is unavailable.\"\"\"\n    with mock.patch('docker.from_env') as mock_docker:\n        mock_client = mock.Mock()\n        mock_docker.return_value = mock_client\n        mock_client.ping.side_effect = DockerException(\"Not available\")\n\n        service = DockerService()\n\n        with pytest.raises(RuntimeError, match=\"Docker is not available\"):\n            service.build_image(\n                dockerfile_path=Path(\"Dockerfile\"),\n                context_path=Path(\".\"),\n                image_name=\"test-image\"\n            )\n```\n\n**4. 镜像推送测试**\n\n```python\ndef test_push_image_with_authentication():\n    \"\"\"Test pushing image with registry authentication.\"\"\"\n    with mock.patch('docker.from_env') as mock_docker:\n        mock_client = mock.Mock()\n        mock_docker.return_value = mock_client\n\n        mock_client.images.push.return_value = [{'status': 'success'}]\n\n        service = DockerService()\n        result = service.push_image(\n            image_name=\"test-image\",\n            registry_url=\"registry.example.com/user\",\n            username=\"testuser\",\n            password=\"testpass\"\n        )\n\n        # Verify login was called\n        mock_client.login.assert_called_once_with(\n            username=\"testuser\",\n            password=\"testpass\",\n            registry=\"registry.example.com/user\"\n        )\n\n        # Verify push was called with correct image name\n        mock_client.images.push.assert_called_once_with(\n            \"registry.example.com/user/test-image\",\n            stream=True,\n            decode=True\n        )\n\n        assert result['pushed_image'] == \"registry.example.com/user/test-image\"\n\ndef test_push_image_password_not_logged():\n    \"\"\"Test that password is never logged during push.\"\"\"\n    with mock.patch('docker.from_env') as mock_docker:\n        mock_client = mock.Mock()\n        mock_docker.return_value = mock_client\n\n        mock_client.images.push.return_value = [{'status': 'success'}]\n\n        service = DockerService(verbose=True)\n        result = service.push_image(\n            image_name=\"test-image\",\n            username=\"testuser\",\n            password=\"secret123\"\n        )\n\n        # Verify password was passed to login but never logged\n        mock_client.login.assert_called_once()\n        assert \"secret123\" not in str(mock_client.login.call_args)\n```\n\n### 集成测试\n\n#### 测试环境要求\n\n- Docker daemon 运行中\n- 测试镜像仓库（可选，用于推送测试）\n- 测试 Dockerfile\n\n#### 集成测试用例\n\n```python\ndef test_build_and_push_integration():\n    \"\"\"End-to-end test: build and push image.\"\"\"\n    service = DockerService(verbose=True)\n\n    # Build image\n    build_result = service.build_image(\n        dockerfile_path=Path(\"test/Dockerfile\"),\n        context_path=Path(\"test\"),\n        image_name=\"integration-test\"\n    )\n\n    assert build_result['image_name'] == \"integration-test:latest\"\n\n    # Verify image exists\n    image_info = service.get_image_info(\"integration-test:latest\")\n    assert image_info['image_name'] == \"integration-test:latest\"\n\n    # Clean up\n    assert service.remove_image(\"integration-test:latest\") is True\n```\n\n### Mock 测试策略\n\n使用 `unittest.mock` 模拟 Docker SDK：\n\n```python\n@pytest.fixture\ndef mock_docker_service():\n    \"\"\"Fixture providing a mocked DockerService.\"\"\"\n    with mock.patch('docker.from_env') as mock_docker:\n        mock_client = mock.Mock()\n        mock_docker.return_value = mock_client\n        mock_client.ping.return_value = True\n        service = DockerService()\n        yield service, mock_client\n```\n\n## 性能考虑\n\n### 内存使用\n\n1. **流式处理**: 构建和推送操作使用流式日志，避免将所有输出加载到内存\n2. **延迟初始化**: Docker 客户端只在需要时初始化\n3. **无状态设计**: 方法调用间不保持状态，减少内存占用\n\n### 并发处理\n\n```python\n# DockerService 是线程安全的（只读操作）\n# 但不建议并发执行构建或推送操作\n# 因为 Docker SDK 本身不是完全线程安全的\n\n# 推荐：为每个操作创建新的 DockerService 实例\nservice1 = DockerService()\nservice2 = DockerService()\n\n# 或者使用队列串行化操作\nfrom queue import Queue\nfrom threading import Thread\n\ndef build_worker(queue: Queue):\n    while True:\n        task = queue.get()\n        service = DockerService()\n        service.build_image(**task)\n        queue.task_done()\n```\n\n### 超时配置\n\n考虑为长时间操作添加超时（未来增强）：\n\n```python\ndef build_image(\n    self,\n    dockerfile_path: Path,\n    context_path: Path,\n    image_name: str,\n    tag: str = \"latest\",\n    build_args: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n    timeout: Optional[int] = None,  # 新增：超时配置\n) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"Build a Docker image with optional timeout.\"\"\"\n    # TODO: 实现超时逻辑\n    pass\n```\n\n## 使用示例\n\n### 基本使用\n\n```python\nfrom agentcube.services.docker_service import DockerService\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# 创建服务实例\ndocker_service = DockerService(verbose=True)\n\n# 检查 Docker 可用性\nif not docker_service.check_docker_available():\n    print(\"Docker is not available\")\n    exit(1)\n\n# 构建镜像\nbuild_result = docker_service.build_image(\n    dockerfile_path=Path(\"Dockerfile\"),\n    context_path=Path(\".\"),\n    image_name=\"myagent\",\n    tag=\"v1.0.0\"\n)\n\nprint(f\"Built image: {build_result['image_name']}\")\nprint(f\"Image ID: {build_result['image_id']}\")\nprint(f\"Size: {build_result['image_size']}\")\n\n# 推送到私有仓库\npush_result = docker_service.push_image(\n    image_name=\"myagent:v1.0.0\",\n    registry_url=\"registry.example.com/username\",\n    username=\"myuser\",\n    password=\"mypassword\"\n)\n\nprint(f\"Pushed: {push_result['pushed_image']}\")\n```\n\n### 在 BuildRuntime 中使用\n\n```python\nclass BuildRuntime:\n    def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None:\n        self.verbose = verbose\n        self.docker_service = DockerService(verbose=verbose)\n\n    def build(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n        \"\"\"Build agent Docker image.\"\"\"\n        metadata = self._load_metadata(workspace_path)\n\n        build_result = self.docker_service.build_image(\n            dockerfile_path=workspace_path / \"Dockerfile\",\n            context_path=workspace_path,\n            image_name=metadata.agent_name,\n            tag=metadata.version or \"latest\",\n            build_args=options.get(\"build_args\")\n        )\n\n        return build_result\n```\n\n### 在 PublishRuntime 中使用\n\n```python\nclass PublishRuntime:\n    def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\") -> None:\n        self.verbose = verbose\n        self.docker_service = DockerService(verbose=verbose)\n        self.provider = provider\n\n    def publish(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n        \"\"\"Publish agent to registry or Kubernetes.\"\"\"\n        metadata = self._load_metadata(workspace_path)\n\n        # 准备镜像\n        image_name = self._prepare_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n\n        # 推送镜像\n        push_result = self.docker_service.push_image(\n            image_name=image_name,\n            registry_url=options.get(\"registry_url\"),\n            username=options.get(\"image_username\"),\n            password=options.get(\"image_password\")\n        )\n\n        # 更新元数据\n        metadata.image = {\n            \"name\": push_result[\"pushed_image\"],\n            \"pushed_at\": push_result[\"push_time\"]\n        }\n        self._save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n\n        return push_result\n```\n\n## 与其他组件的交互\n\n### BuildRuntime 使用\n\n| BuildRuntime → DockerService | 说明 |\n|----------------------------|------|\n| `check_docker_available()` | 构建前检查 Docker 可用性 |\n| `build_image()` | 构建代理镜像 |\n| `get_image_info()` | 获取构建结果信息 |\n| `remove_image()` | 清理失败构建的镜像 |\n\n### PublishRuntime 使用\n\n| PublishRuntime → DockerService | 说明 |\n|-------------------------------|------|\n| `check_docker_available()` | 推送前检查 Docker 可用性 |\n| `push_image()` | 推送镜像到仓库 |\n| `_tag_image_sdk()` | 重新标记镜像用于推送 |\n| `_docker_login_sdk()` | 认证私有仓库 |\n\n### 与 CLI 的集成\n\n```python\n# agentcube/cli/main.py\ndef build(\n    workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\"),\n    proxy: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"-p\", \"--proxy\"),\n    cloud_provider: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--cloud-provider\"),\n    output: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--output\"),\n    verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\"),\n) -> None:\n    \"\"\"Build agent Docker image.\"\"\"\n    try:\n        runtime = BuildRuntime(verbose=verbose)\n        result = runtime.build(\n            workspace_path=Path(workspace),\n            proxy=proxy,\n            cloud_provider=cloud_provider,\n            output_path=output\n        )\n\n        console.print(f\"✓ Built {result['image_name']}\")\n        console.print(f\"  Image ID: {result['image_id']}\")\n        console.print(f\"  Size: {result['image_size']}\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        _handle_error(e, \"build\", verbose)\n```\n\n## 未来增强\n\n### 短期增强（1-2 个月）\n\n1. **超时支持**: 为 `build_image()` 和 `push_image()` 添加超时参数\n2. **进度回调**: 支持进度回调函数，用于 UI 更新\n3. **多架构构建**: 支持 `--platform` 参数构建多架构镜像\n4. **构建缓存优化**: 支持 `--cache-from` 和 `--cache-to` 参数\n\n### 中期增强（3-6 个月）\n\n1. **并行构建**: 支持并行构建多个镜像\n2. **构建历史**: 维护构建历史记录\n3. **镜像分析**: 添加镜像层分析和优化建议\n4. **安全扫描**: 集成镜像安全扫描（如 Trivy）\n\n### 长期增强（6-12 个月）\n\n1. **分布式构建**: 支持远程构建集群\n2. **构建缓存服务**: 集中式构建缓存服务\n3. **镜像签名**: 支持镜像签名和验证\n4. **CI/CD 集成**: 提供更深入的 CI/CD 系统集成\n\n## 故障排查\n\n### 常见问题\n\n**问题 1: Docker daemon 不可用**\n\n```\nRuntimeError: Docker is not available or not running\n```\n\n**解决方案**:\n1. 检查 Docker daemon 是否运行：`docker ps`\n2. 检查 `DOCKER_HOST` 环境变量\n3. 检查 Docker 服务状态：`sudo systemctl status docker`\n4. 重启 Docker 服务：`sudo systemctl restart docker`\n\n**问题 2: 构建失败 - 权限错误**\n\n```\nPermissionError: [Errno 13] Permission denied: 'Dockerfile'\n```\n\n**解决方案**:\n1. 检查文件权限：`ls -la Dockerfile`\n2. 确保当前用户有读取权限\n3. 检查 Docker 用户组权限\n\n**问题 3: 推送失败 - 认证错误**\n\n```\nRuntimeError: Failed to log in to Docker registry: unauthorized\n```\n\n**解决方案**:\n1. 验证用户名和密码\n2. 检查仓库 URL 是否正确\n3. 确认仓库权限设置\n4. 尝试手动登录：`docker login registry.example.com`\n\n**问题 4: 推送失败 - 网络错误**\n\n```\nRuntimeError: Failed to push Docker image: connection timeout\n```\n\n**解决方案**:\n1. 检查网络连接\n2. 配置代理（如适用）\n3. 检查防火墙设置\n4. 增加超时时间\n\n### 调试技巧\n\n**启用详细日志**\n\n```python\ndocker_service = DockerService(verbose=True)\n```\n\n**检查 Docker 日志**\n\n```bash\n# Linux\nsudo journalctl -u docker -f\n\n# macOS (Docker Desktop)\nopen /Applications/Docker.app\n\n# Windows\nGet-Service docker\n```\n\n**验证 Docker 连接**\n\n```python\nservice = DockerService()\nif service.check_docker_available():\n    print(\"Docker is available\")\nelse:\n    print(\"Docker is not available\")\n```\n\n## 总结\n\nDockerService 是 AgentCube CLI 的核心组件之一，为构建和发布工作流提供了统一的 Docker 操作接口。其主要特点包括：\n\n1. **简洁的 API**: 封装 Docker SDK 复杂性，提供简单易用的接口\n2. **完善的错误处理**: 统一的错误处理策略，清晰的错误信息\n3. **安全设计**: 妥善处理敏感信息，验证输入参数\n4. **可观测性**: 支持详细日志模式，便于调试\n5. **可测试性**: 完善的单元测试和集成测试\n6. **可扩展性**: 清晰的架构，便于未来功能增强\n\n通过 DockerService，BuildRuntime 和 PublishRuntime 可以专注于业务逻辑，而将 Docker 操作的复杂性委托给专门的服务层。这种设计提高了代码的可维护性、可测试性和可重用性。","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-024/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-024/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-024/design.md","time":{"start":1775871087577,"end":1775871087589}}}}
